flowchart LR
  Browser[Browser app] --> Backend[/backend or /api/v1]
  Backend --> Vercel[Vercel API adapters]
  Vercel --> Guard[Backend selection guard]
  Guard --> TaskApi[Canonical task-platform handler]
  Guard --> AuditApi[Audit/event handler]
  TaskApi --> TaskService[lib/task-platform]
  AuditApi --> AuditStore[lib/audit]
  TaskService --> Pg[(Supabase or Dockerized Postgres)]
  AuditStore --> Pg
  Compat[Legacy compatibility routes] --> Vercel
  Verify[task-platform verify and drift checker] --> Pg
  Verify --> Monitoring[Dashboards and alerts]
  Guard --> Logs[Structured backend-mode and fallback logs]
